response.original_title: The Call We Carry: Confronting PTSD In The Fire Service | Tacoma Fire Documentary Film
response.overview: Follow the journeys of 4 Tacoma Firefighters, as they share their stories of pain, sacrifice, and resiliency in the midst of an unprecedented call volume increase. The film provides an intimate glimpse into the lives of those who put it all on the line everyday, in an effort to prove once and for all that NO ONE FIGHTS ALONEâ€¦
